Texts.Eng: A functioning teleporter! If I mark it I can return here from a different teleporter at any point.

By markin' this teleporter I can teleport straight back here if n' when I find another teleporter.
Eager. By marking this teleporter I should be able to return to this point from any other teleporter!
If Floran marksss this teleporter Floran can return here from other teleport machines!
If I mark this teleporter I can return here from a different teleporter at any point.
